text: "Plug In Baby" is a 2001 song by Muse. It is the leading single from their second studio album Origin of Symmetry. It went to number 11 in the United Kingdom, number 13 in Scotland, number 40 in France, number 42 in Italy, number 57 in Australia, number 63 in the Netherlands and number 88 in Switzerland. ==Track listing== ==References== Category:2001 songs Category:Muse songs Category:Alternative rock songs
title: Plug In Baby
